<BaseLayout title="Show Me Resistance">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Missouri Deserves Better.</h1>
    <p>
      Show Me Resistance is a platform for exposing destructive legislation,
      corrupt interests, and political hypocrisy across Missouri — with a focus
      on truth, defiance, and action.
    </p>
    <a href="/bill-breakdowns/" class="button">Read the Latest Bill Breakdown</a>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Bill Breakdowns</strong>: Weekly summaries of key bills, their impacts, and progress.</li>
      <li><strong>Vote Tracker</strong>: See how your elected officials are voting — and who they serve.</li>
      <li><strong>Dark Money</strong>: Follow the money behind Missouri politics with donor maps and charts.</li>
      <li><strong>Action Center</strong>: Scripts, resources, and guides to help you take real action.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="subscribe">
    <h2>Stay Connected</h2>
    <p>Sign up for our newsletter to get the latest updates and calls to action.</p>
